        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Poland's system requires full business integration—not ideal for "touch-and-go" nomads. Recommended Hungary's White Card (no registration) or Croatia's DNV (no local tax) instead. Poland best for those willing to integrate into local system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

