    <p class="mb-4">
      Poland has a dual healthcare system. As a registered freelancer paying ZUS, you have access to NFZ (public healthcare). Many expats supplement this with private insurance for faster access and English-speaking doctors.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Healthcare Options</h3>

